Prvo skinite activator odavde: https://downloads.typesafe.com/typesafe-activator/1.3.12/typesafe-activator-1.3.12.zip
To extractujte u neki folder i kopirajte punu putanju
Sad to dodajte u path:
    1. Desni klik na computer -> settings(ili properties nezz sta je) -> advanced settings -> environmental variables(tako nesto)
    2. Nadjite u donjoj listi PATH
    3. Ako je win10 klik na plus i zalijepite taj path + \bin, ako je 7 na kraj dodajte ; i zalijepite path + \bin

Klonirajte ovaj repo negdje.

udjite u root folder i ukucajte u konzoli 'activator run'.

Prvi put ce malo duze trebati da se pokrene dok skine dependencije a posle ce brze.

Pisace na kraju listening on port 9000 i to je to udjete na localhost:9000;
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
API HOST: https://api.sis.kemoke.net

API ROUTES:

POST    /auth/login                 form params: email, password            return: jwt token
POST    /auth/register              form params: username, email, password  return: user

Za ove dolje rute treba staviti u header 'X-Auth-Token' jwt token iz login rute.
Ako istekne token, nevalja ili ga nema izbacice 401 error sa porukom.

# User routes
GET     /users                      form params: none                       return: user list
POST    /users                      form params: username, email, password  return: added user
GET     /users/self                 form params: none                       return: logged in user
GET     /users/:id                  form params: none                       return: user by id
PUT     /users/:id                  form params: username, email            return: edited user
DELETE  /users/:id                  form params: none                       return: "deleted"

# Department routes
GET     /departments                form params: none                       return: dept list
POST    /departments                form params: name                       return: added dept
GET     /departments/:id            form params: none                       return: dept by id
PUT     /departments/:id            form params: name                       return: edited dept
DELETE  /departments/:id            form params: none                       return: "deleted"
